summary: AN ORDINANCE discontinuing as to certain parcels the eminent domain proceedings for the acquisition of land and other property in Lots 97 to 113, inclusive, Seattle Tide Lands, government Lot 4, Section 22, township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.m., Magnolia View Addition No. 2, and Minor's Addition for park and recreation purposes, as provided in Ordinance 96146; superseding said Ordinance to the extent inconsistent and providing for the disposition of the taxable costs.
